data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLER WILL PAY BUYER CLOSING COSTS UP TO $2,000. 
2016 Modern split layout, 2 bed, 2 bath + optional office/3rd bed. Open concept. Expansive granite counters with tons of working space & room to gather. Kitchen island is adorned with beautiful pendant lighting. All Appliances stay. Main bedroom ensuite retreat has double sinks, walk-in shower, extra linen cabinet and spacious walk-in closet. Indoor laundry/mudroom. Washer & Dryer stay. Quiet, low maintenance backyard with extended paver patio and sidewalk, perfect for relaxing/entertaining.  Double garage has storage area, side door to backyard, and soft water plumb ready to go. Membership in the Recreation Centers of Sun City, Inc. offers access to pickleball, billiards, pools, fitness centers and more. Paid thru 10/2024.
